# void /.roadmap — ghostty fork direction
# Rewritten 2026-04-21 after pivot.

# checkpoint
- done [C0] project-init — hexa scaffold 2026-04-21
- done [C1] fork-base   — ghostty → void rebrand 2026-04-21

# scope
# void = ghostty-based AI-native terminal emulator.
# - upstream = ghostty-org/ghostty (zig + swift)
# - direction =
#   (1) grid mode   : native tiling/pane grid as first-class (not plugin)
#   (2) ai-native   : agent I/O, structured stream, tool-call protocol baked
#                     into terminal layer (not wrapper)
#   (3) perf-first  : speed / memory / GPU / syscall budgets tracked per PR

# active phase
- active [P1] grid-mode + input-rebind keybinding
  eta 2026-04-28
  why "native N×M pane grid (tiling, 최우선 기능) + cmd+ctrl+N 누르면 키보드 입력이 N번 셀로 re-bind. 포커스만 옮기는게 아니라 PTY 입력 target 자체가 해당 셀로 스위치."
  features
    - grid-layout   : N×M tiling surface, shared renderer, per-cell cwd/env
    - input-rebind  : cmd+ctrl+1..9 = cell 1..9 로 입력 바인딩 재지정
                      (키 누른 시점부터 모든 stdin → 해당 cell PTY)
                      cmd+ctrl+0       = 전체 broadcast (모든 cell 동시 입력)
                      cmd+ctrl+`       = grid on/off 토글
    - visual-cue    : active cell 테두리/색 강조, 나머지 dim
  ship-target
    - N=2 (horizontal split) MVP 먼저 → N×M 일반화
    - keybinding 은 config 에서 rebind 가능 (하드코딩 X)
- todo   [P2] stack-analysis
  eta 2026-05-05
  why "grid 구현 전 ghostty renderer/apprt/terminal/font 내부 map — 실장 중 diff 최소화"
- todo   [P3] ai-native IO protocol
  why "structured agent I/O channel alongside PTY — tool-call / token-stream aware"
- todo   [P4] perf baseline
  why "capture ghostty baseline benches, set void regression budgets"
- todo   [P5] diverge / upstream strategy
  why "decide which changes feed back to ghostty vs stay void-only"

# non-goals
# - drop-in ghostty replacement (we will diverge in UX)
# - being a shell (void drives shells, does not replace them)
